Source.Contents:
/#
   An entity for defining the agreement executed between the parties and intended to govern all OTC derivatives transactions between those parties.
 #/
record FpML5.recordkeeping.MasterAgreement {
  # An identifier that has been created to identify the master agreement.
  masterAgreementId : string?

  # The agreement executed between the parties and intended to govern product-specific derivatives transactions between those parties.
  masterAgreementType : string?

  # The version of the master agreement.
  masterAgreementVersion : string?

  # The date on which the master agreement was signed.
  masterAgreementDate : date?

}

masterAgreementId.Doc: An identifier that has been created to identify the master agreement.
masterAgreementId.Name: masterAgreementId

masterAgreementType.Doc: The agreement executed between the parties and intended to govern product-specific derivatives transactions between those parties.
masterAgreementType.Name: masterAgreementType

masterAgreementDate.Name: masterAgreementDate
